Installation:
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

 - Should be installed on the same machine that is running the pSB database - if
   not then edit bwctl.cgi to talk to a remote database.  

 - All 3 files (bwctl.cgi, bwctlplot.cgi, and etc/bwctl.tmpl) should be placed
   in web diretories (scripts assume the *same* directory - edit absolute paths
   if not).  The CGI scripts will need exec privs.  
   
Configuration:
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

 - Will need to change path to pSB libraries.  

 - Will need to change the value of the testspecid (see note in bwctl.cgi)

Caveats:
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

 - Some hard coding of the library paths - needs access to a pSB installation
 
 - Hard coded value for the testspecid

